  "_comment": "Example seed config — copy into the news-seed-config ConfigMap (see deployment.yaml). Consumed only when the data volume has no config.json yet (fresh install or PVC loss); UI edits are never overwritten. Only rss_feeds and medium_tags are required; everything else falls back to the defaults shown here.",

